{"tid":2498072,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"學者：仍未「通關」樓市有變數","createTime":"2021-04-21T02:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T05:37:34.000Z","uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d5f32a10c1a89587ee2cedbafbd7d1cabe079e","tid":2498072,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:14:45.000Z","msg":"學者：仍未「通關」樓市有變數<br />\n8小時前<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210421/IHQNWEAHQFCFFJA2QQCWWJSSWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210421%2FIHQNWEAHQFCFFJA2QQCWWJSSWI%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=885993da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210421%2FIHQNWEAHQFCFFJA2QQCWWJSSWI%2F&h=e2febb27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210421/IHQNWEAHQFCFFJA2QQCWWJSSWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n■近月發展商狂推新盤，已消耗市場大量購買力。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自去年港府放寬按揭成數上限後，首季本港樓市交投熾熱，發展商新盤連珠炮發，但港人多個月來都有能力一一承接，然而近月推盤終見有疲態，一手新盤有數次開售反應轉趨冷淡，部份買家靜觀其變，部份轉戰二手，因此變相輪到近期二手樓市交投回暖。不過，香港中文大學商學院高級講師李兆波指，早前一連數個月連環推盤，已經釋放大部份積壓大半年的購買力，加上經濟環境持續疲弱，未來若然遲遲未能「通關」，樓市升勢恐怕仍有變數。<br />\n<br />\n李兆波解釋，目前經濟數據仍然未轉好，積壓的購買力爆發後，接下來的時間，便要視乎本港的經濟基本面，港人有足夠的收入來源支撐，樓市才能繼續走高。然而目前本港經濟數據疲弱，失業率仍然高企，這些問題都要等待「通關」後才能逐漸回復。<br />\n<br />\n李兆波又指，綜觀各國推行疫苗後，疫情都有所紓緩，然而港府推行疫苗的政策滲入太多政治考量，反而適得其反，例如「疫苗快將過期」的說法，令市民抗拒，降低疫苗成效。他料上半年未能「通關」，加上變種病毒存在一定變數，因此樓市仍然有機會受壓，升勢未必持續。"},{"pid":"c26c9e7ca3b378351ef6cd3f7cdacfbea27cde90","tid":2498072,"uid":370843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32fdacb47f70af2e93d692c0468a54986325d71","tid":2498072,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">幾時有封過關姐𨳒AA老母個爛臭花閪</span><br />\n<br />\n當咁多位專家都講源頭來自免檢疫 疫情持續全因政府推免檢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2486766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2486766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf50e28cd5d68b0a47959c048c37c90c969f291a","tid":2498072,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32fdacb47f70af2e93d692c0468a54986325d71","tid":2498072,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:47:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">幾時有封過關姐𨳒AA老母個爛臭花閪</span><br />\n<br />\n當咁多位專家都講源頭來自免檢疫 疫情持續全因政府推免檢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2486766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2486766</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"所以所謂「通關」根本對樓市唔會有大影響"},{"pid":"16f958a5d5073077c9aa39b5e443da91ad3953df","tid":2498072,"uid":289115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"AA回應: 現在主要買家係已經有身分證的新香港人, 根本唔洗通關一樣大把人買樓. 如果下半年通關, 樓市升到去幾高真係估唔到.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa3a82efe8472576a66c093f164a26fc9322dda","tid":2498072,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16f958a5d5073077c9aa39b5e443da91ad3953df","tid":2498072,"uid":289115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:14:03.000Z","msg":"AA回應: 現在主要買家係已經有身分證的新香港人, 根本唔洗通關一樣大把人買樓. 如果下半年通關, 樓市升到去幾高真係估唔到.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:31:25.000Z","msg":"新香港人絕大部分都申請公屋"},{"pid":"33c808986781c2dac5bef5d7dc883464af742511","tid":2498072,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa3a82efe8472576a66c093f164a26fc9322dda","tid":2